    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A partially disassembled Nintendo Switch Lite with an upgraded OLED screen." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dlC-GeWF-HoG9Z9Z8hju527HQFs=/1x0:1672x1114/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73607576/switchliteoled1.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;An early prototype of the Super5 OLED Switch Lite upgrade kit.&lt;/em&gt; | Screenshot: YouTube&lt;/figcaption&gt;
