      &lt;img alt="A bunch of Razer keyboards and laptops flat on a table, viewed from bird’s-eye view, with a Razer Snap Tap logo in the center." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/A3eWHznHUPtjRSp2bRQdCrLbyq4=/160x0:1888x1152/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73607545/KV_snaptap_moreKBandBlades_2048x1152.0.jpg" /&gt;
