&lt;p id="vyvV87"&gt;The new capabilities are part of &lt;a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/arlo-announces-secure-5-next-generation-of-smart-home-security-powered-by-arlo-intelligence-302256439.html"&gt;Arlo Secure 5&lt;/a&gt;, a package of AI-powered features combined with machine learning. Secure 5 is available now to Arlo users in the US, Canada, and Asia-Pacific, with other regions coming soon, according to Ashton Good, senior director of marketing at Arlo.  &lt;/p&gt;
